  "texts": [
    "The left figure shows how the NetVLAD layer implement convolution and VLAD calculation on the input respectively.",
    "The right figure shows the conv-attention layer, which also uses a bilinear operation for computing the attention matrix and the original value module generation, respectively.In terms of the improved structure, our improved attention calculation method is simpler and more efficient compared to the self-attention approach.",
    "In the computation, we avoid the huge amount of computation associated with matrix operations, and since the weights of the convolution are independent of the input data, the number of parameters of the model can be reduced, thus reducing the complexity of the model.",
    "It is worth to note that the computation of the model is not linear with time, the computation can be seen in our analyses in the next section as well as in the FLOPs in our experiments, and the change in time can be seen in the change in FPS in our experiments.",
    "Computational Cost and AnalysisBased on the above theoretical analysis, this paper finds that the process of generating attention is a process of feature mapping and cross-channel information integration."
